[SN]TITLE[SN]
Andy Cosslett set to replace Bill Beaumont as new RFU chairman

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Andy Cosslett is set to replace Bill Beaumont as chairman of the Rugby Football Union.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Cosslett was chairman of England Rugby 2015 - the organising committee for the 2015 World Cup.
The RFU nominations committee has "unanimously" backed Cosslett, after Beaumont was appointed as head of World Rugby.
The 61-year-old's appointment is subject to approval at the next RFU Council on 14 October.
